Module: Pipeline_Run_Time¶

This module containes functionality to read the timing measurement of the pipeline for the report

report.pipeline_run_time.get_pipeline_run_time(obs_id, trigger_mode=False)[source]¶

Function to get the run time of apercal parts

Since parselog is broken and the apercal logfiles have changed due to the parallelisation, this script just reads out the information from the main logfile
